point : it be very difficult to carry out trial by jury if people involve in the case continuously attempt to tamper with the jury , or unduly influence it decision . for example , the uk home office have state that try to protect juror from tamper can be extremely disruptive to the juror themselves , who may in extreme case need police protection 24 hour a day . cases involve international terrorism , drug smuggling or organize crime be the most likely to present such problem 1 . in the infamous trial of italian anarchist vanzetti and sacco , one of the juror have a bomb thrown at his house , despite a huge number of security measure take by the massachusetts government 2 . another example be the 2008 case of a large armed robbery at heathrow . after three mistrial , which cost 22m and the last of which collapse after a serious attempt at jury tampering , it be decide that the case would be try by a judge alone 3 . if eliminate the jury be the only way to ensure that a a trial occurs and b juror be safe , particularly when it be the defendants' fault that a fair trial by jury be untenable , it may be necessary to do so . 
